Pakistan to the world.

1753
02:14:03,875 --> 02:14:06,916
Hamza, the real reason
we asked you to come here is this…

1754
02:14:07,583 --> 02:14:09,333
Years ago, someone told me,

1755
02:14:10,833 --> 02:14:11,875
