1759
02:14:22,208 --> 02:14:24,375
From here on,
you have a free hand, Hamza.

1760
02:14:27,458 --> 02:14:30,416
Courage. Fuel. Revenge.

1761
02:14:33,041 --> 02:14:37,708
Now India will decide Pakistan's fate.

1762
