to Nepal by the 15th of November.

1766
02:15:10,250 --> 02:15:11,166
Here, sir.

1767
02:15:13,750 --> 02:15:15,000
Yaqub Ansari is in Nepal.

1768
02:15:15,083 --> 02:15:18,125
